{"tid":1326432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣7月21日遊行獲警方發出不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-07-17T08:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T10:44:11.000Z","uid":277415,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b046352b495f22e53030731759b88decb2a586a2","tid":1326432,"uid":277415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"民陣7月21日遊行獲警方發出不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n民陣表示，周日集會改為遊行，已獲警方發出不反對通知書。民陣召集人岑子杰表示，7月21日當日會先於下午3時在銅鑼灣維園集合，大約3時半起步，終點會在中環終審法院附近。他表示，選擇這個終點是由於希望爭取成立獨立調查委員會，由法官擔任主席，去調查事件真相。"},{"pid":"5c7056ddfc783b519e874d19e1116cc36a0ac447","tid":1326432,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"[緊急呼籲]［重要野好有用］今晚9點一齊上twitter將黑警濫權揚威國際，警告遊客不要來港旅遊，用經濟壓力逼使政府回應！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1325723/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1325723/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面攬炒<br />\n<br />\n9點一齊一野谷上trending <br />\n#Hongkongwarning #Fthepopo<br />\n<br />\nTwitter見！！！"},{"pid":"75a18b8e07dd360fe6aba2fd8944f9e7d9d2be76","tid":1326432,"uid":186961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"話有信心會獲得不反對通知書咋<br />\n你邊度有消息發出咗啊?"},{"pid":"1beea4b47fced6bfe6fec960ebbfcae6225f351a","tid":1326432,"uid":277415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75a18b8e07dd360fe6aba2fd8944f9e7d9d2be76","tid":1326432,"uid":186961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"話有信心會獲得不反對通知書咋<br />\n你邊度有消息發出咗啊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:07:57.000Z","msg":"民陣記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c147125b7cb557590f956747023fe49f433e2c17","tid":1326432,"uid":152258,"l